Package: NumericTransformation
Type: Package
Title: Transform Categorical data to Numerical 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Rani Basna
Maintainer: The package maintainer <ranibasna@gmail.com>
Description: This package intends to convert categorical features into numerical ones. 
    This will help in employing algorithms and methods that only accept numerical data as input. 
    The main motivation for writing this package is to use in clustering assignments.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
